# Per-machine Claude Code skill symlinks (created by `npx skills add ...`).
# The real skill files live in `.agents/skills/` and ARE tracked. After
# cloning, run `npm run skills:link` (or the npx skills command in CLAUDE.md)
# to recreate the symlinks for your local Claude Code agent.
.claude/skills/impeccable
.claude/skills/frontend-design

# The skill CLI keeps install metadata in .agents/ alongside skills — the
# skills themselves we DO track (lean: impeccable + frontend-design).
.agents/.skills-cache/
.agents/installed.json
